because I brought your brother up.

11:15.125 --> 11:17.394
Oh, no, no, it's not. I'm fine.

11:17.527 --> 11:21.431
I'll be fine if we just keep moving. It's nothing.

11:26.236 --> 11:28.872
You smell like an ashtray.

11:45.622 --> 11:48.392
I'm gonna go down to L.A.
and see what I can find.

11:48.525 --> 11:50.794
We're gonna go past-- What?

11:51.595 --> 11:52.596
Are you getting HBO?

11:52.729 --> 11:54.931
We're supposed to get HBO,
and it's not on mine.

11:55.265 --> 11:57.601
- I don't know. I'm on the phone here.
- I'm sorry.

11:57.734 --> 12:00.537
No, come in and check.

12:00.670 --> 12:02.239
Come in.

12:02.739 --> 12:06.810
Yes, I'm on my way to L.A.
You know, I thought I'd stop by and see you.

12:06.943 --> 12:11.748
No, no, I said Tuesday or Wednesday.
Are you okay?

12:11.882 --> 12:13.683
No, it's just....

12:13.817 --> 12:16.186
All right, no, I'll wait.

12:16.319 --> 12:17.687
<i>The Way We Were is on.</i>

12:19.222 --> 12:22.759
<i>Robert Redford? Barbra Streisand?
The Way We Were.</i>

12:22.893 --> 12:24.561
I don't get out much.

12:25.362 --> 12:27.597
It was 20 years ago.

12:30.200 --> 12:32.335
Oh, great, you got it.

12:32.903 --> 12:36.706
- Do you mind?
- No, please, please.

12:36.840 --> 12:38.675
No, I'm here.

12:39.276 --> 12:42.345
No, I figured we'd come by tomorrow
around noon.

12:42.679 --> 12:45.749
Are you okay? I mean, is it Nick?

12:45.882 --> 12:49.286
No. Fine, fine. All right.

12:49.853 --> 12:53.356
Yeah, no, I'll see you then. Goodbye.

12:54.524 --> 12:55.859
