in another life.

15:19.836 --> 15:24.040
- Anyway, I didn't get it.
- It's all right. There's always time.

15:24.374 --> 15:26.109
Yeah.

15:27.410 --> 15:30.714
Is that why you left New York?
Because that bartender did you wrong?

15:30.847 --> 15:32.716
Something like that.

15:35.085 --> 15:38.622
Eight o'clock tomorrow, okay?
If you wanna get to Pittsburgh by 12.

15:41.458 --> 15:43.960
- Good night.
- Good night.

15:44.094 --> 15:46.062
