he has a drink and he gets confused.

17:48.718 --> 17:54.157
Holly, if you cleaned this fucking place up,
maybe I'd fucking be able to find my shit!

17:55.759 --> 17:59.662
- What the fuck are you doing here?
- Hello, Nick. I'm just passing through.

17:59.796 --> 18:01.598
