- Frank, this guy uptown. A friend.

19:25.048 --> 19:26.182
Hey, Nick.

19:26.316 --> 19:30.386
Jane, let me close this.
Where's his number?

19:30.720 --> 19:32.322
It's on the wall.

19:33.890 --> 19:36.025
