19:48.037 --> 19:49.772
- You know how it is.
- I understand.

19:49.906 --> 19:53.843
Is Frank there? Yeah.

19:57.113 --> 19:58.948
Frank.

19:59.082 --> 20:03.219
You score an eighth off me Tuesday night?
Yeah.

20:03.353 --> 20:05.021
How much?

20:05.922 --> 20:08.925
