01:46:07.412 --> 01:46:09.113
Elaine.

01:46:09.847 --> 01:46:11.249
What?

01:46:11.382 --> 01:46:14.285
- Shut up.
- Jerry.

01:49:34.285 --> 01:49:36.721
- Ready to go?
- Yeah.

01:49:37.054 --> 01:49:40.057
Now, you better be back for Christmas.
Mary Todd's expecting you.

01:49:40.191 --> 01:49:41.492
Yeah, I will.

01:49:41.626 --> 01:49:45.029
Call me as soon as you get to L.A.
I wanna know how the audition went.

01:49:45.162 --> 01:49:46.597
Okay, Mom.

